{"data":[{"date":"09:36 21/06","title":"Diego Costa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iran","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/diego-costa-khang-dinh-khong-choi-xau-thu-mon-iran.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Diego Costa th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng may nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN Costa tranh bong voi Iran\" title=\"TBN Costa tranh bong voi Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/HLV-Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iran</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Iran \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Trong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat La Roja \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Iran. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi c\u00fa ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Iran l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Diego Costa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0, Costa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh n\u00f3i: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iran \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho TBN b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00f9 nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc th\u00edch h\u1ee3p&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iran Alireza Beiranvand. &quot;V\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Beiranvand, t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec bi\u1ebft xung quanh m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1y quay. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Beiranvand ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;, Costa qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Costa di\u1ec5n ra trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 tuy nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool Jamie Redknapp&nbsp;th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a Costa l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Hierro \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Iran kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Diego Costa, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; run r\u1ea9y gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Iran song T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Tr\u1eadn Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-421-189119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/TBN-an-mung-tran-thang-Iran-1-0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-421-189119.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/HLV-Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. TBN ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Diego Costa m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"415","checkdouble":"189135"},{"date":"09:51 21/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-trung-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm.</h2><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/DT-U19-Viet-Nam-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-Trung-Quoc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u00f2n gi\u00e3 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Meizhou v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0. V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp Meizhou 5-0. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24/6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26/6. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 14/7 t\u1ea1i Jakarta (Indonesia). \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, Th\u00e1i Lan, Singapore, L\u00e0o, Philippines. B\u1ea3ng B c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Malaysia, Myanmar, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, Campuchia v\u00e0 Brunei.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia v\u00e0 Malaysia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, c\u0169ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/DT-U19-Viet-Nam-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-Trung-Quoc-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam-168-186505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam-168-186505.html\">Indonesia g\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng kh\u1ee7ng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T U19 Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Ba Lan, &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; Egy Maulana \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"414","checkdouble":"189137"},{"date":"10:56 21/06","title":"Carvajal l\u00ean \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iran","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/carvajal-len-an-chien-thuat-tieu-cuc-cua-iran.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t C\u0110V vui t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Iran gi\u01a1 bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef \"T\u00e2y Ban Nha 0-6 Iran\" nh\u01b0ng sau 90 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kazan Arena kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V gi\u01a1 bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef TBN 0-6 Iran trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Iran b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u0110V gi\u01a1 bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef TBN 0-6 Iran trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Iran b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/1529513660172_lc_galleryImage_epa06824226_Spanish_socce.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c C\u0110V T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hoa trang an tuong cua mot CDV Tay Ban Nha.\" title=\"H\u00f3a trang \u1ea5n