enter\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/35744087_2190201994547920_3279057563122925568_n.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kim Jin-seo v\u00e0 Rimario th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, BL\u0110 HAGL \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i\u00a0 binh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 HAGL. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar Moreira. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o HAGL \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2016. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh t\u1eebng ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian Osmar g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi HAGL kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Osmar ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho SLNA tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Osmar, HAGL c\u00f2n th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng\u00a0Vincent Bossou sinh n\u0103m 1986. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i V-League. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Togo tham d\u1ef1 hai VCK CAN 2013 v\u00e0 2017. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n,\u00a0Vincent Bossou \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu-168-189067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/6/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu-168-189067.html\">CLB HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh xung quanh vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn d\u00ednh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t l\u1ea7n hai v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"412","checkdouble":"189139"},{"date":"10:20 21/06","title":"B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u1eb7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Iran gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai hai lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Ma-r\u1ed1c. Trong s\u1ed1 ba \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Iran l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang B World Cup 2018 sau hai luot tran dau tien.\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/bang-b.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong tay nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (B\u0110N) v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (TBN) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Iran vs B\u0110N s\u1ebd mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean h\u00e3y nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn quy t\u1eafc x\u00e9t th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng VCK&nbsp;World Cup 2018. N\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nhau, FIFA s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/b\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nhau th\u00ec ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iran thua B\u0110N</h2>\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, <em><strong>B\u0110N v\u00e0 TBN m\u1eb7c nhi\u00ean gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</strong></em>, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa TBN vs Ma-r\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ca Bo Dao Nha va Tay Ban Nha van co nguy co bi loai tai bang B World Cup 2018.\" title=\"C\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>N\u1ebfu Iran thua trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, B\u0110N v\u00e0 TBN s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iran h\u00f2a B\u0110N</h2>\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu TBN kh\u00f4ng thua Ma-r\u1ed1c, <strong><em>TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</em></strong>.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neu Iran hoa BDN, tran dau giua TBN vs Ma-roc se dinh doat suat di tiep tai bang B World Cup 2018.\" title=\"N\u1ebfu Iran h\u00f2a B\u0110N, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa TBN vs Ma-r\u1ed1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/tbn-vs-maroc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>N\u1ebfu Iran h\u00f2a B\u0110N, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa TBN vs Ma-r\u1ed1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu TBN thua Ma-r\u1ed1c, hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* TBN thua Ma-r\u1ed1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u (0-1, 1-2,...), Iran v\u00e0 TBN s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 0.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u00eau ch\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, TBN \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n v\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n, trong khi Iran m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Iran ph\u1ea3i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u0110N, trong khi TBN ch\u1ec9 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma-r\u1ed1c.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu TBN c\u1ee9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ma-r\u1ed1c, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Iran c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam. <em><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</strong></em>.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- N\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng nhau v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e9t t\u1edbi. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, <strong><em>Iran s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</em></strong> do \u0111\u00e3 thua TBN&nbsp;0-1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* TBN thua Ma-r\u1ed1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb hai b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean (0-2, 1-3, 2-4,...), <em><strong>TBN s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</strong></em> khi c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng k\u00e9m Iran v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iran th\u1eafng B\u0110N</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, Iran s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. TBN ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng thua Ma r\u1ed1c c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, <em><strong>B\u0110N s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</strong></em>.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Iran se gianh suat di tiep tai bang B World Cup 2018 neu danh bai Bo Dao Nha o tran dau cuoi.\" title=\"\u0110T Iran s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/iran-5.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Iran s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p TBN c\u0169ng thua Ma-r\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi B\u0110N khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra:<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 gi\u1ed1ng nhau (0-1, 1-2,...). Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m (4), b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng h\u00f2a 3-3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, FIFA s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed fair-play \u1edf c\u1ea3 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 sau: C\u1ee9 1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng - tr\u1eeb 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp (2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng) - tr\u1eeb 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp - tr\u1eeb 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp - tr\u1eeb 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 th\u00ec B\u0110N&nbsp;\u0111ang thua thi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng (t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 -2 \u0111i\u1ec3m) trong khi TBN&nbsp;m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn 1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng (-1 \u0111i\u1ec3m)<br />\r\n&nbsp; </div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* TBN v\u00e0 B\u0110N kh\u00f4ng thua v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 th\u00ec <em><strong>\u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o thua \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</strong></em> do k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng - b\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; run r\u1ea9y gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span></di