eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-iran-cay-cu-sau-that-bai-day-cay-dang-truoc-tbn-421-189118.html\">HLV Iran cay c\u00fa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thang-chat-vat-truoc-iran-hlv-tbn-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-421-189117.html\">Th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, HLV TBN c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"410","checkdouble":"189141"},{"date":"10:55 21/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 21/6: N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/ngay-hom-nay-216.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (21/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nN\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1edbi ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \"tr\u1ea3m\" Mesut Oezil.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/anh13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u0111ang lan r\u1ed9ng sau khi \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Mexico 0-1 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n, nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u HLV Joachim Loew \"tr\u1ea3m\" Mesut Oezil. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 10 g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua Mexico, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i mu\u1ed1n \u00f4ng Loew d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf anh.</div>\r\n<h2>Diego Costa ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"Trong hi\u1ec7p 1, Iran ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00f9 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Beiranvand, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng b\u1edfi bi\u1ebft xung quanh m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1y quay. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Beiranvand ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\", ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha chia s\u1ebb.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diego-costa-khang-dinh-khong-choi-xau-thu-mon-iran-421-189135.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/diego-costa-khang-dinh-khong-choi-xau-thu-mon-iran.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/diego-costa-khang-dinh-khong-choi-xau-thu-mon-iran-421-189135.html\">Diego Costa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iran</span><br>\r\n<span>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Diego Costa th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng may nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Hierro c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Iran ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u1edfi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7nl\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\", hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Fernando Hierro tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thang-chat-vat-truoc-iran-hlv-tbn-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-421-189117.html\">Th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, HLV TBN c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV c\u1ee7a Iran ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi thua T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u201cT\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y run s\u1ee3\u201d, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Carlos Queiroz tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau khi Iran thua T\u00e2y Ban Nha 0-1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-iran-cay-cu-sau-that-bai-day-cay-dang-truoc-tbn-421-189118.html\">HLV Iran cay c\u00fa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Rakitic l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng \u0111e d\u1ecda Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Croatia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic - ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, v\u1eeba tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Lionel Messi - th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Argentina. Rakitic v\u00e0 Messi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Barcelona.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Truc-tiep-tin-nong-World-Cup-21-6-Rakitic-lon-tieng-de-doa-Messi-messirakitic-cropped_1qodgd3hbhjh317biopagzp0vo-1529523168-776-width660height371.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u1eadt kh\u1edbp vai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">HLV \u0110T Anh, \u00f4ng Gareth Southgate b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. \u00d4ng Southgate b\u1ecb tr\u1eadt kh\u1edbp vai. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y may m\u1eafn b\u1edfi m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u201cTam s\u01b0\u201d. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"409","checkdouble":"189142"},{"date":"11:25 21/06","title":"L\u00fd do h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nu\u00f4i \"r\u00e2u d\u00ea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Iran v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRonaldo nu\u00f4i ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u d\u00ea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd troll k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Messi sau c\u00fa hattrick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u1edbi l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1, m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u &ldquo;con d\u00ea&rdquo; (goat = xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i) m\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u01b0u \u00e1i d\u00e0nh cho Leo Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1o ph\u1ea7n r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1edbi \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, khi anh lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh &ldquo;m\u00e0y r\u00e2u nh\u1eb5n nh\u1ee5i&rdquo; tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang, hay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ricardo Quaresma v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo kh\u00e1 l\u0103n t\u0103n v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u (trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb9p trai c\u1ee7a anh gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u\" title=\"Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/cristiano-ronaldo-cropped_1f5krpdeo1lzf11ohj93twdos5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Quaresma&rdquo; &ndash; CR7 cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf trong ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm h\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea1o r\u00e2u v\u1ea3 n\u1ea3y ra m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Quaresma r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i ph\u1ea7n r\u00e2u \u1edf c\u1eb1m (goatee) cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n sau \u0111\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng 1, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp hattrick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111em l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn cho CR7, khi anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V n\u1eef, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y &ldquo;h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng&rdquo;. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng th\u00e0nh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o anh c\u0169ng ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam clip Cantona ch\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec3u Messi, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Neymar<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/20/cantona.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-ronaldo-lai-toa-sang-nhung-421-189093.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/du-am-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-ronaldo-lai-toa-sang-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-ronaldo-lai-toa-sang-nhung-421-189093.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Ma R\u1ed1c: Ronaldo l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Ma R\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 ra Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 B\u0110N nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n &ldquo;th\u00f3t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\">B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u1eb7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Iran gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-10-maroc-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189089.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-10-maroc-bang-b-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-10-maroc-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189089.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Mar\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Patricio c\u00f9ng ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"408","checkdouble":"189143"},{"date":"11:52 21/06","title":"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran ch\u1eedi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t v\u00ec thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/cau-thu-iran-chui-trong-tai-sap-mat-vi-thien-vi-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea1p xi\u1ebfc\u201d \u2013 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Ronaldo.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 fan Ronaldo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Iran v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7, si\u00eau sao Cris Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng khi\u1ebfn CR7 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu C\u0110V c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t&hellip; tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, th\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m c\u00e2n n\u1ea3y m\u1ef1c Mark Geiger. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn Iran vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao Iran t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Ronaldo\" title=\"tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/cau-thu-iran-chui-trong-tai-sap-mat-vi-thien-vi-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao Iran t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Amrabat, v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch, khi \u0111\u00f2i xin \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Iran cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u00f4ng ta c\u00f3 quen Ronaldo t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u00f4ng ta r\u1ea5t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb Pepe r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng ta th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn xin x\u1ecf Ronaldo chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u. Chuy\u1ec7n qu\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1eady? Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup hay \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea1p xi\u1ebfc?&rdquo; &ndash; ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Amrabat&nbsp; t\u1ecf ra b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c&nbsp;tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb Ronaldo.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Amrabat&nbsp; l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Watford, nh\u01b0ng anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i La Liga \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Leganes. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Iran v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 Cris Ronaldo &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0110T k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam clip Cantona ch\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec3u CR7 v\u00e0 Messi<br>\r\n</strong><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\" alt=\"\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\">L\u00fd do h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u d\u00ea</span><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Iran v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/bang-b-world-cup-2018-kich-ban-nao-de-tay-ban-nha-va-bo-dao-nha-bi-loai-466-189140.html\">B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ho\u1eb7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Iran gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-10-maroc-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189089.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-10-maroc-bang-b-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-10-maroc-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189089.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Mar\u1ed1c (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Patricio c\u00f9ng ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"407","checkdouble":"189144"},{"date":"11:30 21/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/16/nhung-ly-do-dt-tay-ban-nha-kho-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Iran. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, La Roja r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018 </span>b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. V\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng tr\u1ea3i qua 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Iran. Th\u1eafng 1-0, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 La Roja \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2010 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eadn ra b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u2018nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2\u2019 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2014 hay EURO 2016, nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0110T TBN \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Nhung-ly-do-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-kho-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ef1u binh t\u1eebng gi\u00fap TBN v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2012 nh\u01b0 Ramos, Pique, Busquets, Silva, Iniesta th\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 De Gea, Carvajal, Koke, Isco, Asensio,... V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Costa<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Costa \u0111ang l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ghi b\u00e0n l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV Hierro tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng La Roja. Tuy nhi\u00ean vi\u1ec7c Costa b\u1ecb c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 Costa r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Iago Aspas song ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngo\u00e0i 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean, trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a TBN c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Lucas Vazquez v\u00e0 Rodrigo Moreno, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f9ng sinh n\u0103m 1991 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eebng th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2008 -2012 nh\u1edd s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi \u2018c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng\u2019 Xavi- Iniesta. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Barca \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n sung s\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u01b0a TBN tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i titki-taka bi\u1ebfn \u1ea3o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u qua th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, tiki-taka c\u0169ng d\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i trong ti\u1ec1m th\u1ee9c. \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhanh h\u01a1n, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva va Andres Iniesta\" title=\"David Silva va Andres Iniesta\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/David-Silva-va-Andres-Iniesta.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 TBN v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u01b0 Iniesta hay David Silva</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u0129 nhi\u00ean Real kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i tiki-taka v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n,\u00a0tinh qu\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ec1 cao s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u00f3m. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. Trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m qua, c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-0 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc Maroc, Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh. V\u00e0 khi b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang may r\u1ee7i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. HLV Hierro<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, TBN kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00ec h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd HLV Hierro ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00fang 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Hierro l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf HLV, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 0 tr\u00f2n tr\u0129nh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Hierro noi ve tran BDN vs TBN\" title=\"Fernando Hierro n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn B\u0110N vs TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/hlv-hierro-khong-muon-dt-tay-ban-nha-di-vao-vet-xe-do-cua-nguoi-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Fernando Hierro c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a TBN l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh HLV Hierro c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Julen Lopetegui t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng trong hai n\u0103m qua. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Lopetegui, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi 61 b\u00e0n trong 20 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi v\u1ecb HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/diego-costa-khang-dinh-khong-choi-xau-thu-mon-iran.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Hierro \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Iran kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Diego Costa, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/HLV-Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. TBN ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Diego Costa m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-421-189119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/TBN-an-mung-tran-thang-Iran-1-0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-421-189119.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d run r\u1ea9y gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Iran song T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Tr\u1eadn Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"406","checkdouble":"189146"},{"date":"08:07 21/06","title":"Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-neymar-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 quan khi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat PSG \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-neymar-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i ban \u0111\u1ea7u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham gia t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1ea5y l\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i anh s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Neymar ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean\u00a0Twitter: ''Neymar \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m nay 20/6. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin vui v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Brazil v\u00e0 gi\u1edbi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf World Cup g\u1eb7p Costa Rica v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 22/6. L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Brazil, Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho \u2018nh\u1eefng v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Neymar b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ecb \u0111au tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau khi ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu t\u1edbi 10 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i\u00a0c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 r\u00e1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u khi\u1ebfn Neymar kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u, d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-brazil-ra-quan-that-vong-o-world-cup-2018-466-188838.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/3-ly-do-khien-brazil-ra-quan-that-vong-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-khien-brazil-ra-quan-that-vong-o-world-cup-2018-466-188838.html\">3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Brazil ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn Selecao b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-11-thuy-sy-421-188829.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-11-thuy-sy.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-11-thuy-sy-421-188829.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-1 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9</span><br>\r\nBrazil \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"405","checkdouble":"189126"},{"date":"08:29 21/06","title":"HLV Argentina b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hlv-argentina-bao-ve-messi-truoc-tran-dau-thu-hai-voi-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Arrgentina t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jorge Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lionel Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Argentina b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018 khi anh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng qu\u1ea3 penalty khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Argentina b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi Croatia  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Argentina b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi Croatia  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/hlv-argentina-bao-ve-messi-truoc-tran-dau-thu-hai-voi-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Lionel  Messi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Messi, v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh so v\u1edbi Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp hat-trick b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV \u0110T Argentina Jorge Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c'Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u1eb1n v\u1eb7t sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3. Ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i. \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Khi b\u1ea1n ghi b\u00e0n cho Argentina, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng khi Argentina thua, th\u00ec l\u1ed7i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Messi. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Messi r\u1eb1ng \u2018\u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a 40 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Argentina. B\u1ea1n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, t\u00f4i m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, \u0110T Argentina m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng nhau, ni\u1ec1m vui c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n\u2019. Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m cho k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Argentina'', \u00f4ng Sampaoli cho hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c HLV Sampaoli \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Messi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong m\u1ecfi M10 s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p Croatia. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Argentina s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u1eaft chiu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-messi-421-189109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/rakitic-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-canh-bao-dong-doi-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-messi-421-189109.html\">Rakitic c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Messi</span><br>\r\nIvan Rakitic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-nho-rakitic-tu-van-de-bat-chet-messi-421-188900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-croatia-nho-rakitic-tu-van-de-bat-chet-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-nho-rakitic-tu-van-de-bat-chet-messi-421-188900.html\">HLV Croatia nh\u1edd sao Barca t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Messi</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u01afCV v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Argentina, HLV Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng bao g\u1ed3m vi\u1ec7c nh\u1edd h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Ivan Rakitic t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u00e1ch \u2018b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft\u2019 si\u00eau sao Lionel...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-cay-cu-chi-trich-loi-choi-lay-loi-cua-iceland-421-188805.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/messi-cay-cu-chi-trich-loi-choi-lay-loi-cua-iceland.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-cay-cu-chi-trich-loi-choi-lay-loi-cua-iceland-421-188805.html\">Messi cay c\u00fa ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i l\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Iceland</span><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Barcelona kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a Argentina 1-1 Iceland trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"404","checkdouble":"189127"},{"date":"08:32 21/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/argentina-vs-croatia-01h00-ngay-226-chua-cung-bat-luc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ea5ng c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf, xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i \u2013 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh cho Leo Messi, nh\u01b0ng theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia, \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 cho El Pulga.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa d\u00ea (goat) nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Leo Messi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Hay ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, anh g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 penalty b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Iceland, sau \u0111\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/video-cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-doan-clip-king-eric-chui-deu-messi-ronaldo-va-neymar-421-189032.html\" target=\"_blank\">Messi b\u1ecb huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Cantona\u2026 khinh b\u1ec9</span>. X\u00e9t theo v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Argentina.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \"ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\"\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/maradona-bao-ve-messi-chi-trich-nhan-to-khac-cua-argentina-421-188795.html\" target=\"_blank\">Diego Maradona cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho Messi v\u00ec \u201cx\u1ecbt pen\u201d</span>, b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u (d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 27 l\u1ea7n, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng 78%), nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua Messi, ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Albiceleste t\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Argentina-vs-Croatia-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>N\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 tham gia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Mascherano v\u00e0 Biglia, Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng ph\u00f2ng tuy\u1ebfn Iceland. Ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, nh\u1eefng Di Maria hay Meza c\u0169ng qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh Messi c\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Caballero qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ean t\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Argentina, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u00e0o, ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn Iceland. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t Leo Messi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Halldorsson \u2013 v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n. Trong khi, Sampaoli c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u201cnha s\u0129 b\u00e1n th\u1eddi gian\u201d Heimir Hallgrimsson. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, \u0111i\u1ec1u Iceland \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n, Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. HLV Sampaoli, v\u00ec v\u1eady s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. B\u1edfi m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, Albiceleste l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Argentina-vs-Croatia-(01h00-ngay-226)-Chua-cung-bat-luc-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Argentina, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd - \u0110T Croatia l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap Modric v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u01b0ng v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Argentina tr\u01b0\u1ee3t ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng 78% v\u00e0 s\u00fat 27 qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca-ro may m\u1eafn khi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Nigeria. B\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Modric l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t 11m. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Croatia \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Argentina l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng Croatia c\u1ee7a anh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n b\u00ean ph\u00eda Croatia c\u0169ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 226) Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Argentina-vs-Croatia-(01h00-ngay-226)-Chua-cung-bat-luc-hinh-anh-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sao-ac-milan-bi-duoi-thang-co-khoi-world-cup-2018-vi-ly-do-lang-xet-421-188837.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nikola Kalinic \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u1eb3ng c\u1ed5 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span>, sau khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi l\u00fd do... \u0111au l\u01b0ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi HLV Zlatko Dalic, k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 World Cup v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm Mario Mandzukic.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Argentina ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Croatia v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eefng Modric hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Rakitic (\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi t\u1ea1i Barca) \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, ho\u1eb7c Lionel Messi \u0111\u00f3ng vai Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf (ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Cris Ronaldo trong tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha), b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng \u2013 <strong>Argentina kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Preview Argentina vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2162018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Argentina b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup (t\u00ednh sau 90 ph\u00fat).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Argentina vs Croatia g\u1eb7p nhau 4 l\u1ea7n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Argentina th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 1, thua 1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Argentina h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Croatia trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ea1i World Cup (1-0, 1998)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Messi l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 (11 l\u1ea7n), ghi 0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Messi ghi 2 b\u00e0n sau 2 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Croatia b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Croatia thua c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p trong c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- N\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, Vedran Corluka s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n th\u1ee9 100 cho \u0110T Croatia.</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, HLV Sampaoli bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd xoay sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 Di Maria, Meza c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Croatia \u0111ang v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. C\u00f3 ch\u0103ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 thay 1-2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch gi\u1eef v\u1eefng khung th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arrgentina (3-4-1-2)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">23.Caballero</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2.Mercado \u2013 17.Otamendi \u2013 3.Tagliafico</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">18.Salvio \u2013 14.Mascherano \u2013 15.Perez \u2013 5.Biglia</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">10.Messi</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">22.Pavon \u2013 19.Aguero</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia (4-2-3-1)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">23.Subasic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2.Vrsaljko \u2013 6.Lovren \u2013 21.Vida \u2013 3.Strinic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">7.Rakitic \u2013 11.Brozovic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4.Perisic \u2013 10.Modric \u2013 18.Rebic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">17.Mandzukic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Argentina vs Croatia: 1-1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Argentina vs Croatia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Argentina vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Argentina-vs-Croatia-(3-4-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Argentina vs Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-doan-clip-king-eric-chui-deu-messi-ronaldo-va-neymar-421-189032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/video-cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-doan-clip-king-eric-chui-deu-messi-ronaldo-va-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-doan-clip-king-eric-chui-deu-messi-ronaldo-va-neymar-421-189032.html\">Video: C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi \u0111o\u1ea1n clip King Eric ch\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec3u Messi, Ronaldo v\u00e0 Neymar</span><br>\r\n3 ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Eric Cantona chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi, Ronaldo...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-gio-hay-goi-messi-la-miss-penalty-421-188688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tu-gio-hay-goi-messi-la-miss-penalty.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-gio-hay-goi-messi-la-miss-penalty-421-188688.html\">T\u1eeb gi\u1edd, h\u00e3y g\u1ecdi Messi l\u00e0 Miss Penalty</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch s\u00e2u cay nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Argentina-vs-Croatia-(01h00-ngay-226)-Chua-cung-bat-luc-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-ra-quan-that-vong-va-bai-hoc-ve-su-hieu-qua-421-188678.html\">Argentina ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nD\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u2013 Argentina. C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u2013 Argentina. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u2013 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Argentina. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"403","checkdouble":"189128"},{"date":"08:50 21/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (19h ng\u00e0y 21/6): V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho \u201cL\u00ednh ch\u00ec\u201d?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-australia-19h-ngay-216-ve-di-tiep-cho-linh-chi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia v\u00e0 Peru kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u201cL\u00ednh ch\u00ec\u201d. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Age Hareide ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cueva \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Peru kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Yussuf Poulsen. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Eriksen, Poulsen b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00f4ng minh \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (19h ng\u00e0y 216) b\u1ea3ng C World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (19h ng\u00e0y 216) b\u1ea3ng C World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Dan-Mach-vs-Australia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 27 ph\u00fat, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf s\u00e2n Saransk. H\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Peru.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng so v\u1edbi Australia, \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2006.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi HLV Ange Postecoglou b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11, Bert van Marwijk \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAustralia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 t\u1ea1i Kazan.<br>\r\n<h2>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch s\u1ed1ng nh\u1edd Eriksen</h2>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/dt-dan-mach-o-world-cup-2018-trong-ca-vao-christian-eriksen-421-188043.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eriksen l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng</span> trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Poulsen ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEriksen \u0111\u00e3 in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 17 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (12 b\u00e0n, 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o). C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Christian Eriksen dang la niem hy vong lon nhat cua bong da Dan Mach\" title=\"Christian Eriksen \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/peru-du-kha-nang-bat-chet-christian-eriksen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Eriksen s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd v\u1eady, HLV Age Hareide c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Eriksen. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 nh\u1edd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Australia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch coi nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 William Kvist v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Peru, \u00f4ng Hareide \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong tay nh\u01b0 Kasper Schmeichel, Simon Kjaer, Christian Eriksen hay Andreas Christensen. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia:</strong><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee9 4 gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Australia v\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a (\u0110an M\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng 2, Australia th\u1eafng 1)<br>\r\n- Australia \u0111\u00e3 thua 7/9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf World Cup<br>\r\n- \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n \u1edf World Cup<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 28 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m<br>\r\n- Christian Eriksen g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o 17 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 14 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (12 b\u00e0n, 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o)<br>\r\n- Australia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup, th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn<br>\r\n- Australia m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 1 l\u1ea7n trong 14 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Dan Mach vs Australia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Dan-Mach-vs-Australia-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-4-1-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 1-0</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tim-cahill-can-duoc-ra-san-trong-tran-gap-dan-mach-421-189077.html\">Tim Cahill c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-australia-that-vong-truoc-tran-thua-phap-421-188660.html\">HLV Australia th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"402","checkdouble":"189131"},{"date":"02:16 21/06","title":"Thomas Muller ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/thomas-muller-tiet-lo-tinh-hinh-dt-duc-sau-tran-thua-mexico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich kh\u1eb3ngd \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn l\u1edbn sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Mexico. Trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Thomas-Muller-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Mexico ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf Hirving Lozano m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Mexico \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTh\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u1ecd thua Mexico, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb chia r\u1ebd sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, theo \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico c\u00f9ng HLV Low b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n chia r\u1ebd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Muller kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich kh\u1eb3ngd \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Muller 2\" title=\"Thomas Muller 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/bai-du-thi-co-xe-tang-duc-thomas-muller.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Muller kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1ea5t \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Mexico c\u0169ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong b\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"401","checkdouble":"189112"}]}